$ Excel VBA: range.formula2

`range.formula2` allows to specify a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/formulas without → Microsoft/Office/Excel/formulas/operators/intersection#excel-add-f-without-int-sect[automatically adding the intersection operator].

sa:

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/formulas#excel-formula-eval-mode[Excel formula evaluation modes]

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range/formula[`range.formula`]

  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range[`range`] object.
